Company Overview
Dongguan Fulida Rubber Co., Ltd. is located in the center of Dongguan City, Guangdong Province, China. It was estabished in 2009, but the founder has been specialized in this field for more than ten years. We are a professional manufacturer of various kinds of computer mouse pads, professional game mouse pads and game gloves, rubber roll materials, bar mats, yoga mats and some other anti-slip mats and promotional gifts. We have different materials for all our productions, such as natural rubber, neoprene rubber, nitrile rubber, SBR, EVA, PP, PVC foam, 3D lenticular, gel, silicon, alumium, polyester fabric, non-woven fabric, lycra, polished fabric and so on. The material, specification, design, logo printing and packing are all can be customized. Your OEM production are very welcome.Through the efforts of our entire staff, we have become a professional manufacturer of mouse pads. The whole of our production is under strict quality control and supervision, all of the raw materials we use are compliant with CE&SGS&ROHS tests . Covering a building area of 3000 square meters, we have a complete set of advanced machines, equipments and a perfect group of professional technicians and senior personnel. With excellent quality, reasonable price and good service, our company offers natural foam rubber roll material, various kinds of high-class mouse pads, computer game gloves, bar mats, yoga mats, coasters, desk pads and so on. They are natural, odourless, environmentally friendly, non-toxic and harmless to human body. The beautiful appearance and individual design also attract many customers. As mouse pads become one of todays best promotional tools and gifts, which help to guide your customers to your companys website or bring your products information to the public, therefore custom-made designs, logos and OEM orders are very welcome. We truly hope and believe that our high quality, reasonably priced products and sincere service will meet your business requirements, and satisfy your different demands. We are looking forward to your kindly inquiries and cooperations, and hope to build long-term and win-win business relationships with you. For more details, please do not hesitate to contact us.
